headline: Will the NFL Bring the Magic Back to Disney Stock?
summary: The NFL and Disney have tied themselves more closely together with the NFL getting 10% of ESPN in exchange for the NFL Network, RedZone distribution rights, and more assets. Will it make Disney a winner in streaming?

headline: Spending for Executive Protection Is on the Rise
summary: The median security expenditure for executives climbed to $106,500 in 2024 from $48,500 in 2020. The biggest risks are seen in the tech, communication services, healthcare, and energy sectors.
